'''AAA'''（读作“3A”）為[[電子遊戲產業|電子遊戲產業]]中的一個分野，没有准确定义，一般认为是指投入高製作費用與高[[市場行銷|行銷]]成本的游戏<ref name="AAA">{{cite book|last=Kent|first=Steven|authorlink=Steven L. Kent|title=The Ultimate History of Video Games: From Pong to Pokémon and Beyond- The Story That Touched Our Lives and Changed the World|url=https://archive.org/details/ultimatehistoryo0000kent|year=2001|edition=First|publisher=Prima Publishing|location=Roseville, California|isbn=0-7615-3643-4}}</ref><ref name="definition1">{{cite book|last1=Demaria|first1=Rusel|last2=Wilson|first2=John|title=High Score!: The Illustrated History of Electronic Games |url=https://archive.org/details/highscoreillustr0000dema|year=2002|edition=First|publisher=McGraw-Hill Osborne Media|location=USA|isbn= 0-07-222428-2}}</ref><ref name="definition2">{{cite book|last=J.P.Wolf, Mark|first=|authorlink=Mark J.P.Wolf|title=The Video Game Explosion: A History from PONG to PlayStation and Beyond|year=2002|edition=First|publisher=Greenwood Press|location=London|isbn= 0240811461}}</ref><ref name="gamasutra.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/130722/e3_report_the_path_to_creating_.php |title=E3 Report: The Path to Creating AAA Games |publisher=gamasutra.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-30 |archive-date=2013-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110165433/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/130722/e3_report_the_path_to_creating_.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其中行銷成本也是巨大的開銷，宣傳費用甚至可能超過製作遊戲本身的花費<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.videogamer.com/news/modern-warfare-2-cost-40-50-million |title=Modern Warfare 2 cost $40-$50 million|date=2009-11-19|author=James Orry |accessdate=2019-01-14 |archive-date=2019-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114100542/https://www.videogamer.com/news/modern-warfare-2-cost-40-50-million |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據[[inXile娛樂|inXile娛樂]][[CEO|CEO]] Brian Fargo的訪談，以相對AAA低一階的AA級遊戲來說，在2018年僅以製作費用估量，AA級的上限已達到2000萬美元水準<ref>[https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2018-11-19-inxile-acquired-by-microsoft-the-interview InXile acquired by Microsoft: the interview] {{Wayback|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2018-11-19-inxile-acquired-by-microsoft-the-interview |date=20181221211549 }} Eurogamer.net (19/11/2018)</ref>；由上述數字可知，AAA級遊戲的製作費用無疑是一筆相對更高的巨額投資。根據前[[索尼互動娛樂|索尼互動娛樂]][[CEO|CEO]] Shawn Layden的訪談，就2020年市場中的大多數AAA級遊戲來看，僅估算製作費用已達8000萬至1億5000萬美元的水準，並需要長達5年的遊戲製作時間<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2020-06-23-shawn-layden-gamelab |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-11-30 |archive-date=2022-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220130231206/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2020-06-23-shawn-layden-gamelab }}</ref>。

== 起源 ==

1983年伴随着[[雅达利冲击|雅达利冲击]]事件，整个[[1983年美国游戏业萧条事件|北美游戏行业进入大萧条]]。于是，早期现代主义的电子游戏在80年代出现，游戏公司急需一个崭新而准确的标准术语来区分游戏的优劣。[[任天堂|任天堂]]等公司第一批创建品質审核机制，若游戏通过这个审核则意味着该游戏的品質有一定保证<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.com/consumer/licensed.jsp |title=Licensed and Unlicensed Products |publisher=nintendo.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-30 |archive-date=2014-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140114074453/http://www.nintendo.com/consumer/licensed.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 Beam Software的员工Alfred Milgrom则重新诠释高品质的定义——零缺陷<ref name="Nintendoattitude">{{cite book|last=Donovan, Tristan|first=|authorlink=|title=Replay: The History of Video Games|year=2010|edition=First|publisher=Yellow Ant|location=East Sussex,UK|isbn=978-0-9565072-2-8}}</ref>。这在当时的游戏业内都是不敢想象的。此时业内对游戏品質的评判多还是通过数字或者文字评论，而没有相关的专有词汇来描述、分类。

于是從90年代開始，在美国的一些游戏產业会议中（如[[CES|CES]]、[[游戏开发者大会|CGDC]]、[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]和其他私人会议），有些企业开始使用AAA一詞來描述自家遊戲作品的規模與水準<ref name="definition3">{{cite book|last=Rusel Demaria and John Wilson|first=|authorlink=Demaria, Rusel and Wilson, Johnny Lee |title=High Score!: The Illustrated History of Electronic |url=https://archive.org/details/highscoreillustr0000dema|year=2002|edition=First|publisher=McGraw-Hill Osborne Media|location=USA|isbn= 0-07-222428-2}}</ref>。这源自於美国的学术评分方式：A为最高，F表示最低。游戏领域AAA有时可视同电影中的“[[大片|大片]]”<ref name="AAA_PR">{{cite book|last=Steinberg, Scott |first=|authorlink=|title=The definitive guide: Videogame marketing and PR|year=2007|edition=First|publisher= iUniverse, Inc|location=USA|isbn= 0-07-222428-2}}</ref>。进入千禧年以来，许多发行商尚在游戏发行前，就将之冠上AAA<ref name="gamasutra.com" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/05/15/ubisoft-has-2-new-aaa-games-coming/ |title=ubisoft-has-2-new-aaa-games-coming |publisher=ign.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2014-01-30 |archive-date=2014-03-05 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20140305060255/http://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/05/15/ubisoft-has-2-new-aaa-games-coming/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/06/10/black-tusk-creating-aaa-game-for-xbox-one// |title=black-tusk-creating-aaa-game-for-xbox-one |publisher=joystick.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131123941/http://www.joystiq.com/2013/06/10/black-tusk-creating-aaa-game-for-xbox-one/ |archive-date=2014-01-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，并投入巨额的研发與行销预算<ref name="bigbudgetAAA">{{cite book|last=Thomas, David; Orland, Kyle and Steinberg, Scott |first=|authorlink=|title=The Videogame Style Guide and Reference Manual|year=2007|edition=First|publisher=Lulu.com/IGJA |location=USA|isbn=978-0595433711}}</ref>。

